full_summary:
# Government Tender Announcement
**Title**: Geomatics Services
**Reference Number**: CB-3896-60381657
**Amendment Number**: 1
**Solicitation Number**: NRCan-5000069156
**Publication Date**: 2023-02-17
**Tender Closing Date**: 2023-03-06
**Expected Contract Start Date**: 2023-04-01
**Expected Contract End Date**: 2023-03-31

**Tender Description**:

Natural Resources Canada (NRCan) is seeking Task-Based Informatics Professional Services (TBIPS) under Supply Arrangement (SA) EN578-170432. The contract will be awarded for a period of one year ending March 31, 2025, with the option to extend for three additional one-year periods.

The services required include:

* Geomatics Analyst (G.1) – Level 2
* Geomatics Specialist (G.2) – Level 2
* Geographic Information System (GIS) Applications Analyst (G.3) – Level 3
* GIS Application Architect (G.4) – Level 3
* GIS Data Architect (G.5) – Level 2
* GIS Project Manager (G.8) – Level 3

**Procurement Information**

* Procurement Category: SRV (Services)
* Procurement Method: Competitive – Selective Tendering
* Tender Status: Expired
* Regions of Opportunity: Worldwide
* Regions of Service Delivery: Remote Offsite
* Contracting Entity: Natural Resources Canada
* Contact Information:

Catherine Boilard
catherine.boilard@nrcan-rncan.gc.ca
(418) 254-4882

**Attachments**

The tender notice and associated documentation can be found at:

https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/3896/notice-of-proposed-procurement-%28npp-nrcan-5000069156-172937_0.pdf
https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/3896/avis-de-projet-de-marche-%28apm-nrcan-50000069156-172937.pdf

Note: I assume that this is a tender that needs to be submitted by a potential supplier. If this is not the case, please let me know so I can adjust my response accordingly.
